	{"heading":"Stardate 2412.9 (Conclusion)",
	"commentary":"<p>Alternate Cruisers are truly insane! Because of how potent our setup is, even against Hard difficulty, there was virtually no risk of failing this playthrough! Considering what a Bottom 7% first battle and even a Bottom 4% final battle did for us, this was easily a decisive success.</p><p>We are a little low on adventures with the pre-packaged Doomsday Machine scenarios. Granted; neither Large map has yet been conquered beyond Hard difficulty, nor has Small been conquered on Good Luck difficulty, nor have we cleared a run as the Replicators. Still, we may take advantage of Space Empires Anthology's modular system... and maybe experiment with this scenario on a Talon board.</p>",
